ukr:
Tis true without lying, certain and most true.
That which is below is like that which is above
and that which is above is like that which is below
to do the miracles of one only thing.
And as all things have been and arose from one by the mediation of one: 
so all things have their birth from this one thing by adaptation.
en:
Tis true without lying, certain and most true.
That which is below is like that which is above
and that which is above is like that which is below
to do the miracles of one only thing.
And as all things have been and arose from one by the mediation of one: 
so all things have their birth from this one thing by adaptation.

ukr:
The necessity of concealing the Art is
one of the chief anxieties of alchemists. 
We are sworn to secrecy by heaven and earth and hell,
by the four elements, by the height and the depth,
by Hermes, by Anubis,and by the howlings of Kerkoros.
An oath has been required of us to reveal
nothing clearly to any uninitiated being.
en:
The necessity of concealing the Art is
one of the chief anxieties of alchemists. 
We are sworn to secrecy by heaven and earth and hell,
by the four elements, by the height and the depth,
by Hermes, by Anubis,and by the howlings of Kerkoros.
An oath has been required of us to reveal
nothing clearly to any uninitiated being.

ukr: Thence is born a spirit white as snow,\nand another spirit red as blood,\nwhich two spirits are contained in a third hidden thing.
en: Thence is born a spirit white as snow, \nand another spirit red as blood,\nwhich two spirits are contained in a third hidden thing.

ukr: Heed my warning or death and decay will follow.
en: Heed my warning or death and decay will follow.

ukr:
The definition of death is the disjunction of the composite, 
but there is no disjunction of that which is simple, for it is one.
Death consists in the separation of the soul from the body,
because anything formed out of two, three,
or four components must disintegrate, and this is death.
Understand, further, that no complex substance which lacks fire eats, 
drinks, or sleeps, because in all things which have a spirit 
fire is that which eats.
en:
The definition of death is the disjunction of the composite, 
but there is no disjunction of that which is simple, for it is one.
Death consists in the separation of the soul from the body,
because anything formed out of two, three,
or four components must disintegrate, and this is death.
Understand, further, that no complex substance which lacks fire eats, 
drinks, or sleeps, because in all things which have a spirit 
fire is that which eats.

ukr:
And the Lord spake, saying,
'First shalt hou take out the Holy Pin.
Then, shalt thou count to three. No more. No less.
Three shalt be the number thou shalt count, 
and the number of the counting shall be three. 
Four shalt thou not count, neither count thou two,
excepting that thou then proceed to three.
Five is right out. Once at the number three, 
being the third number be reached, then,
lobbest thou thy Holy Hand Grenade of Antioch towards 
thy foe, who, being naughty in My sight, shall snuff it.'
en:
And the Lord spake, saying,
'First shalt hou take out the Holy Pin.
Then, shalt thou count to three. No more. No less.
Three shalt be the number thou shalt count, 
and the number of the counting shall be three. 
Four shalt thou not count, neither count thou two,
excepting that thou then proceed to three.
Five is right out. Once at the number three, 
being the third number be reached, then,
lobbest thou thy Holy Hand Grenade of Antioch towards 
thy foe, who, being naughty in My sight, shall snuff it.'

ukr:
Some Alchemists fancy that the work from beginning 
to end is a mere idle entertainment; but those who 
make it so will reap what they have sown - nothing. 
We know that next to the Divine Blessing,
and the discovery of the proper foundation,
nothing is so important as unwearied industry
and perseverance in this First Operation.
It is no wonder, then, that so many students
of this Art are reduced to beggary;
they are afraid of work, and look upon our Art as 
mere sport for their leisure moments. For no labour 
is more tedious than that which the preparatory part 
of our enterprise demands.
en:
Some Alchemists fancy that the work from beginning 
to end is a mere idle entertainment; but those who 
make it so will reap what they have sown - nothing. 
We know that next to the Divine Blessing,
and the discovery of the proper foundation,
nothing is so important as unwearied industry
and perseverance in this First Operation.
It is no wonder, then, that so many students
of this Art are reduced to beggary;
they are afraid of work, and look upon our Art as 
mere sport for their leisure moments. For no labour 
is more tedious than that which the preparatory part 
of our enterprise demands.

ukr:
Among those who devote themselves to the transmutation of metals,
however, there can be no such thing as mediocrity of attainment.
A person who studies this Art, must have either everything or nothing.
An Alchemist who knows only half their craft, reaps nothing but disappointment 
and waste of time and money; moreover, they lay themselves open to the mockery 
of those who despise our Art. Those, indeed, who succeed in reaching the goal 
of the Magistery, have not only infinite riches, but the means of continued 
life and health. Hence it is the most popular of all pursuits.
en:
Among those who devote themselves to the transmutation of metals,
however, there can be no such thing as mediocrity of attainment.
A person who studies this Art, must have either everything or nothing.
An Alchemist who knows only half their craft, reaps nothing but disappointment 
and waste of time and money; moreover, they lay themselves open to the mockery 
of those who despise our Art. Those, indeed, who succeed in reaching the goal 
of the Magistery, have not only infinite riches, but the means of continued 
life and health. Hence it is the most popular of all pursuits.

ukr:
Woe unto all ye fools! 
How ignorant are ye of this Art, for which ye would die if ye knew it! 
I swear to you that if kings were familiar with it, 
none of us would ever attain this thing. 
O how this nature changeth body into spirit! 
O how admirable is Nature, how she presides over all, and overcomes all.
en:
Woe unto all ye fools! 
How ignorant are ye of this Art, for which ye would die if ye knew it! 
I swear to you that if kings were familiar with it, 
none of us would ever attain this thing. 
O how this nature changeth body into spirit! 
O how admirable is Nature, how she presides over all, and overcomes all.

ukr:
In this way, then, Nature generates by means of 
this sulphur the different kinds of metals in the 
veins of the earth, according to the diversity of 
degrees and alterations.
en:
In this way, then, Nature generates by means of 
this sulphur the different kinds of metals in the 
veins of the earth, according to the diversity of 
degrees and alterations.

ukr:
Vizjmitj, kaže vin nam, zolotyj kaminj, z'jednajte joğo z ğumorom, jakyj je
 nezminnoju vodoju, postavte joğo, v posudyni svoïj, na tenditnyj voğonj,
poky ne stanetjsja rozridžennja.
 Potim polyšte joğo, poky voda ne vysoxne,
ta zmišajte pisok z vodoju, pislja pidsyljte voğonj, poky ne vysoxne vono,
ta stane zemleju. Koly ce ğotovo, rozumijte, ŝo tut počynajetjsja arkanum.
Robitj ce bağato raziv, poky dvi tretyny vody ne zğynutj, i javljatjsja vam koljory.
en:
Take, he tells us, the stone of gold, combine with humour which is
permanent water, set in its vessel, over a gentle fire until liquefaction
takes place. Then leave it until the water dries, and the sand and
water are combined, one with another;  then let the fire be more intense
than before, until it again becomes dry, and is made earth. When this is done,
understand that here is the beginning of the arcanum;  but do this many times, 
until two-thirds of the water perish, and colours manifest unto you.

ukr:
If all the mountains were of silver and gold, what would 
they profit a man who lives in constant fear of death? 
Hence there cannot be in the whole world anything better than our Medicine,
which has power to heal all the diseases of the flesh.
en:
If all the mountains were of silver and gold, what would 
they profit a man who lives in constant fear of death? 
Hence there cannot be in the whole world anything better than our Medicine,
which has power to heal all the diseases of the flesh.

Makes a projectile fly back and forth

ukr: Dejakyj čas navkolo vas obertajutjsja visim oxoronnyx voğniv
en: Eight guarding lights rotate around you for a time

ukr: Vyklykaje čotyrjox voğnjanyx svitljačkiv, na dopomoğu vam u bytvi

ukr: Čakluje nastupne zaklynannja tryči, ale z menšoju škodoju

ukr: Čakluje nastupne zaklynannja 10 raziv, ale z menšoju škodoju

en: Makes a projectile leave a trail of copies of itself

en: A good tool for cutting meat. Also has some magical properties...

ukr: Kydaje sporovu kapsulu, jaka prykripljujetjsja do poverxni, a potim roste i vybuxaje šypamy
en: Summons a spore pod that attaches to a surface and then grows and explodes into spikes

en: It was theorized that the source of qualia would be transferred …But it turns out it was the whole body all along.

ukr: Stvorjuje propanovyj balon. Budjte oberežni zi svoïmy bažannjamy.
en: Summons a propane tank. Be careful what you wish for.

ukr: Vyklykaje spektraljnu palyčku, kotra vypuskaje velyčeznyj prominj svitla
en: A spectral wand is summoned that casts a huge beam of light
Summons a self-propeled mine cart loaded with explosives

ukr: Vyklykaje kryxitnu beztilesnu istotu vam na dopomoğu. Vona može čakluvaty syljniši zaklynannja, zaležno vid toğo, jakoï škody vy zaznaly.

ukr: Zmušuje snarjad vypuskaty buljbaškovi iskry, koly vin vidskakuje

ukr: Snarjad, ŝo prynosytj neŝastja vsim, u koğo vlučytj
en: A projectile that brings bad luck to anyone it hits
Hearts bestow double the maximum health.

ukr: Vidteper u kožnij Svjaŝennij ğori vy znajdete dodatkovu zdibnistj.
en: From now on you will find an extra perk in every Holy Mountain.

ukr: Koly vy obyrajete odnu zdibnistj, je 50% jmovirnistj, ŝo inši ne znyknutj.
en: When you pick a perk, there's a 50% chance the others won't disappear.

ukr: Istoty stajutj biljš ağresyvnymy odyn do odnoğo.
en: Creatures become more aggressive towards each other.

ukr: Istoty stajutj biljš družnimy odyn do odnoğo.
en: Creatures become more friendly towards each other.

ukr: Vy sojuznyky z vypadkovoju ğrupoju voroğiv.
en: You're allies with a random enemy group.

ukr: Vaši kopnjaky zavdajutj biljše škody ta kraŝe vidštovxujutj.
en: Your kicks deal extra damage and knockback.

ukr: Biljšistj snarjadiv omynajutj vas, ale vy otrymujete troxy biljše škody vid snarjadiv.
en: Most projectiles are repulsed by your presence, but you take slightly more projectile damage.

ukr: Vaša krov — slyz, ale slyz biljše ne spoviljnjuje vas, i vy majete biljšyj opir škodi vid snarjadiv.
en: You bleed slime, but slime no longer slows you down.

ukr: Vaše OZ bude prymnožene, ale vy biljše ne zmožete joğo popovnyty.
en: Your HP has been multiplied but you can no longer regain HP.

ukr: Vaša krov — leğkozajmysta nafta, ale vy ne vrazlyvi do voğnju.
Zoloto, jake vy bačyly, biljše ne znykaje z časom.
en: Gold that you've seen no longer disappears over time.

ukr: Vidštovxuvannja biljše ne dije na vas.

en: Your spells knock enemies around with more force.

ukr: Vaši zaklynannja majutj menšyj rozkyd ta biljše škody, ale majutj zbiljšenu zatrymku čakluvannja.
en: Your spells have lower spread, but they push you back more.

ukr: Majže vsi vaši zaklynannja vidskakujutj ta tryvajutj dovše.
en: Almost all your spells bounce around.

ukr: Vaši zaklynannja povertajutjsja do vas bumeranğom, ale otrymujutj dodatkovu švydkistj i zavdajutj biljše škody.
en: Almost all your spells arc towards you. You gain higher projectile resistance.

ukr: Vy vypuskajete straxitlyvi macaky pry otrymanni škody ta otrymujete 25% oporu škodi vid snarjadiv.
en: You call a monstrous tentacle against those who harm you.

ukr: U vas vyrostajutj cikavi dodatkovi kincivky, jaki borjutjsja za vas.
en: You grow curious additional limbs that fight for you.

ukr: Pry smerti voroğy vypuskajutj ŝuriv, ŝo budutj služyty vam! Vsi ŝury — vaši druzi.
en: Enemies that die near you summon hungry rats to serve your bidding.

ukr: U vas vyrostajutj straxitlyvi na vyğljad kincivky, jaki b'jutjsja za vas.
en: You grow disturbing looking limbs that fight for you.

ukr: Dodaje vypadkove pryv'jazane zaklynannja do palyčky u vašyx rukax. Maksymum 4.
en: A random Always Cast spell is added to the wand in your hand, with a maximum of 5.

ukr: Biljšistj palyčok budutj bez tasuvannja. Palyčky u vašomu inventari takož budutj bez tasuvannja.
en: From now on there are no more shuffling wands. The wands you carry with you turn into non-shufflers too.

ukr: Palyčky ne možna zminjuvaty, ale z voroğiv možutj vypadaty kryvavi ğroši.
en: Wands cannot be tinkered with, but enemies may drop blood money.

ukr: Vaši zaklynannja dubljuutjsja pry zitknenni z pereškodamy.
en: Your spells duplicate as they hit obstacles.

ukr: Vaši zaklynannja zavdajutj 3-kratnoï škody, koly u vas menše niž 25 OZ, abo 25% vid maksymaljnoğo zapasu zdorov'ja.
en: Your spells deal 3x damage when you're under 25 HP or 25% of maximum health.

ukr: Vy ukladajete myr zi svoïmy boğamy.
en: You make peace with your Gods.

ukr: Kryvavi ğroši vypadajutj, koly smertj je neŝasnym vypadkom.
en: Blood money is dropped when death is an accident.

ukr: Pid čas levitaciï vy zalyšajete za soboju slid z mağičnyx iskor, jaki zavdajutj škody istotam pry kontakti.
en: When levitating, you leave a trail of magical sparks that harm passing creatures.

ukr: Vykorystannja ŝojno znajdenyx i ne modyfikovanyx palyčok zciljuje vas.
en: Firing newly found and unmodified wands heals you.

ukr: Vaše jestvo keruje povitrjam navkolo vas!
en: Your being controls the air around you!
That was not the best of ideas
I wonder if there's anything inside?
The egg is covered in slime

ukr: Kažutj, ŝob dosjağty velykoğo bağatstva, treba buty ğotovym zrujnuvaty samu osnovu cjoğo svitu. Odnak, jakŝo xtosj ce zrobytj, vin bude prokljatyj. Ale ž ïxnja vlasna žadibnistj sama po sobi i je prokljattjam...
en: It is said that to attain great wealth one must be ready to break the very foundation of this world. However, would one do that, they'd be cursed. Yet their own greed is a curse on its own...

ukr: Runičnyj kaminj z syljnoju mağičnoju auroju. Joğo tak i xočetjsja kopnuty.
en: A runestone with a strong magical aura. You feel like kicking it.

ukr: Ključ dzvenytj, ale čoğosj ne vystačaje...
en: The key hums, but something is missing...

ukr: Kiš šepoče tajemnyci j obicjanky. Vin ğotovyj.
en: The key whispers secrets and promises, it is ready.

ukr: Cja palyčka perelomylasja navpil, ale vse ŝe potriskuje mağičnoju enerğijeju
en: This wand has snapped in half but it still crackles with magical energy

ukr: Cej malenjkyj kaminčyk zmušuje vas vidčuvaty sebe duže zarjadženym.
en: This small rock makes you feel very charged.

ukr: Cej kryxitnyj kaminj vyğljadaje duže palkym, ale pry dotyku vidčuvajetjsja lyše pryjemne teplo.
en: This tiny rock looks most fiery, but when touched only a pleasant warmth can be felt.

ukr: Cej kryxitnyj nebesnyj ob'jekt maje syljne ğravitacijne tjažinnja.
en: This tiny celestial object has a strong gravitational pull.

ukr: Cej nevelykyj kaminj tverdyj i micnyj, ale, zdajetjsja, nače vin fontanuje vodoju.
en: This small rock is hard and solid, yet seems to be gushing with water.

ukr: Kydajte joğo dlja otrymannja riznyx pryziv!

en: You discovered an orb of true Knowledge
You discovered an orb of corrupted Knowledge

ukr: Vy znajšly znajomu sferu istynnyx znanj
en: You found a familiar orb of true Knowledge
Secrets of endless lava have been unlocked to you.
Secrets of Earth's anger have been unlocked to you.
Secrets of otherworldly life have been unlocked to you.

ukr: Tajemnyci cilkovytoğo znyŝennja buly vidkryti dlja vas.
en: Secrets of utter destruction have been unlocked to you.

ukr: Tajemnyci pekla buly vidkryti dlja vas.
en: Secrets of Undeath have been unlocked to you.

ukr: Tajemnyci voğnju i sirky buly vidkryti dlja vas.
en: Secrets of fire and brimstone have been unlocked to you.

ukr: Tajemnyci Spirali buly vidkryti dlja vas.
en: Secrets of the Spiral have been unlocked to you.

ukr: Tajemnyci ğrozovyx nebes buly vidkryti dlja vas.
en: Secrets of stormy skies have been unlocked to you.

ukr: Tajemnyci radosti buly vidkryti dlja vas.
en: Secrets of jubilation have been unlocked to you.

ukr: Tajemnyci pryxovanoï nebezpeky buly vidkryty dlja vas.
en: Secrets of hidden danger have been unlocked to you.

ukr: Tajemnyci vidbudovy buly vidkryti dlja vas.
en: Secrets of rebuilding have been unlocked to you.

ukr: Cja tajemnycja ne povynna bula buty dostupnoju dlja vas.
en: This secret should not have been available for you.

ukr: Tajemnyci velykoğo znyŝennja buly vidkryti dlja vas.
en: Secrets of great undoing have been unlocked to you.

ukr:
Ce eksperymentaljna funkcija.
Vykorystovujte na vlasnyj ryzyk. Zapuskajte mody lyše z perevirenyx džerel!
Najvyŝi uvimkneni mody bude zavantaženo peršymy.
Klacnitj na nazvu moda, ŝob uvimknuty/vymknuty joğo.
en:
This is an experimental feature.
Use at your own risk. Only run mods from trusted sources!
Upmost enabled mod will be loaded first.
Click mod name to enable/disable the mod.

ukr: Vykorystovujte mody na svij strax i ryzyk. Zapuskajte mody lyše z perevirenyx džerel!\nModyfikaciï vyŝe budutj zavantaženi peršymy.\nKlacnitj na nazvu moda, ŝob uvimknuty/vymknuty joğo.
en: Use mods at your own risk. Only run mods from trusted sources!\nUpmost enabled mod will be loaded first.\nClick mod name to enable/disable the mod.

ukr: Zminy naberutj čynnosti pislja nastupnoğo perezapusku.
en: Changes will be applied on next restart.

ukr: Poperedžennja: Dejaki modyfikaciï možutj poğano perenosyty uvimknennja/vymknennja u ğri, čerez ce možutj z'javytysja pomylky, dyvnosti ta ğra može vyletity.
en: Warning: some mods may not handle enabling/disabling ingame well - weirdness, bugs or crashes may occur.

ukr: Počaty novu ğru z aktyvnymy modyfikacijamy
en: Start a new game with enabled mods active

ukr: U cij versiï zmineno povedinku modiv.\nVsi mody potribno povtorno uvimknuty u menju «Modyfikaciï».
en: This version changes how mods behave.\nMods need to be re-enabled via the “Mods” menu.

ukr:
Cej mod zaprosyv dodatkovi pryvileï.
Jakŝo joğo uvimknuty, vin matyme povnyj dostup do vašoğo komp'jutera,
navitj bez vykorystannja možlyvyx vrazlyvostej u kodi ğry.
Vy vpevneni, ŝo xočete dovirjaty cjomu modu?
en:
This mod has requested extra privileges.
If enabled, it has full access to your computer,
even without using possible exploits in the game code.
Are you sure you want to trust this mod?

ukr: Cej mod zaprosyv dodatkovi pryvileï.\nNebezpečni modyfikaciï majutj buty uvimkneni dlja zapusku cjoğo moda.
en: This mod has requested extra privileges.\nUnsafe mods need to be enabled to run this mod.

ukr: Mody majsterni ne možutj buty uvimkneni, jakŝo nebezpečni modyfikaciï dozvoleno.
en: Workshop mods cannot be enabled while unsafe mods are on.

ukr: Cej mod nespravnyj i ne može buty uvimknenyj [Kod pomylky #N0174H4X].
en: This mod is broken and cannot be enabled [Error code #N0174H4X].

ukr: Uvimknennja nebezpečnyx modyfikacij nadaje usim vstanovlenym modyfikacijam povnyj dostup do vašoğo komp'jutera.\nVy vpevneni?
en: Enabling unsafe mods gives all installed mods full access to your computer.\nAre you sure?

ukr: Uvimknennja nebezpečnyx modyfikacij nadaje vsim vstanovlenym modyfikacijam povnyj dostup do vašoğo komp'jutera.\nVy vpevneni?
en: Enabling unsafe mods gives all installed mods full access to your computer.\nAre you sure?

ukr: Vynykly pomylky pid čas inicializaciï modiv:
\nZapustitj ğru z cym modom čerez menju «Nova ğra».
en: \nPlay this mod via the “New game” menu.

ukr: \nUvimknitj cej pereklad čerez punkt «Mova» v menju «Nalaštuvannja».
en: \nEnable this translation via “Language” in the “Options” menu.

ukr: Nemožlyvo aktyvuvaty dekiljka modyfikacij z identyfikatorom «$0».
en: Cannot enable multiple mods with the id “$0”.
This is a Steam Workshop mod.

ukr: Ce eksperymentaljna funkcija.\nVykorystovujte na svij strax i ryzyk!\nVam varto zapuskaty modyfikaciï tiljky z perevirenyx džerel.
en: This is an experimental feature.\nUse is at your own risk!\nYou should only run mods from trusted sources.

ukr: Vykorystovujte modyfikacij na svij strax i ryzyk!\nVam varto zapuskaty modyfikaciï tiljky z perevirenyx džerel.
en: Use of mods is at your own risk!\nYou should only run mods from trusted sources.

ukr: Vynykly pomylky pid čas inicializaciï takyx modyfikacij: $0
en: There were errors when initializing following mods: $0

ukr: Zavantažennja vmistu majsterni «$0»\nJakŝo zavantažennja ne vidbuvajetjsja,\nmožlyvo, vam slid zminyty ïxnij priorytet u spysku zavantaženj biblioteky Steam.
en: Downloading Workshop content $0\nIf the downloads don't seem to progress,\nyou might need to change their priority in the Steam library downloads list.

ukr: Cej mod ne testuvavsja z ostannjoju versijeju interfejsu modynğu.
en: This mod has not been tested with the latest version of the modding interface.

ukr:
Cej mod buv stvorenyj z novišoju versijeju interfejsu modynğu.
Može potrebuvaty novišu versiju ğry.
Abo, možlyvo, rozrobnyk modyfikaciï prosto vykorystovuje novu versiju ğry,
ta vin sumisnyj z potočnoju.
en: This mod has been built with a never version of the modding interface.\nA never version of the game might be required.

ukr: Avtozberežennja znajdeno. Sxože, ŝo ğra vyletila.\nČy varto sprobuvaty vidnovyty avtozberežennja?
en: Autosave found. Looks like the game crashed?\nShould the game attempt to restore the autosave?

ukr: Dejaki mody buly uvimkneni ta, možlyvo, spryčynyly zbij.
en: Some mods were enabled and might have caused the crash.

ukr: Noita znaxodytjsja v rannjomu dostupi, my postarajemosja ce vypravyty. :/
en: Noita is in early access, we'll try to fix this. :/

ukr: Natysnitj B na kontroleri, ŝob skynuty do počatkovyx
en: Press B on a control to reset it to default

ukr:
Laskavo prosymo do Noita Epilogue Update!
Kolysj Noita bula ğroju rannjoğo dostupu, tož my xočemo vyslovyty velyčeznu podjaku vsim,
xto ğrav u Noita protjağom peršoğo roku ïï isnuvannja. Vaši vidğuky buly bezcinnymy!
A vsim novym ğravcjam Noita... Laskavo prosymo i bažajemo udači!

en:
Welcome to Noita 1.0!
Noita used be an Early Access game, so we want to send a huge thank you to all of you
who played Noita during its first year. Your feedback has been invaluable!
And to all the new Noita players... Welcome and best of luck!
- Devs

ukr:
OSNOVNE:
Novyj režym ğry Ŝodennyj trenuvaljnyj zabiğ.
Inteğracija z Twitch - nexaj ğljadači strimu zrobljatj vašu ğru ŝe biljš xaotyčnoju.
Modyfikatory bioma - biomy inodi troxy vidriznjajutjsja vid zvyčnoğo vyğljadu. \Dejaki biomy majutj imitovani temperaturni efekty.
Bağato nalaštuvanj i dopovnenj ğejmpleja ta interfejsu.
Vizualjni ta zvukovi pokraŝennja.
Novi zaklynannja, vminnja, voroğy, materialy, sekrety, zvuky ta bağato inšoğo.
Biljše 15 novyx muzyčnyx trekiv: Pidzemni džunğli, Sxovyŝe, Xram Mystectva ta inši.
Optymizacija produktyvnosti i vypravlennja pomylok.
Pererobka menju nalaštuvanj.
en:
HIGHLIGHTS:
New Daily Practice Run game mode.
Twitch integration - let stream viewers make your game even more more chaotic.
Biome modifiers - biomes are sometimes a bit different from the usual form.
Some biomes have simulated temperature effects.
Lots of gameplay and UI tweaks and additions.
Visual and audio enhancements.
New spells, perks, enemies, materials, secrets, sounds and more.
Over 15 new music music tracks: Underground Jungle, Vault, Temple of the Art and more.
Performance optimizations and bug fixes.
Options menu overhaul.

ukr:
«Tut ja v bezpeci. Ja v bezpeci.
Ja zalyšyv inšyx pozadu, i ja zamknuv svoï doslidžennja tak, ŝob tiljky ti, xto maje spravžnje rozuminnja, moğly dosjağty ïx.
Meni ne varto xvyljuvatysja. Dopoky ja protystojatymu spokusi, ja budu v bezpeci.
Ja znaju svoï meži. Tut ja daleko vid nyx.

Meni ne varto xvyljuvatysja.»
en:
”Here I'm safe. I am safe.
I left the others behind, and I have locked my research so that only those with real understanding can reach it.
I should not worry. As long as I resist the temptation, I will be safe.
I know my limits. Here I am far away from them.

I should not worry.”

en: Your spells home towards yourself for a time.

ukr: Vaši zaklynannja zavdajutj biljše škody, majutj menšyj rozkyd ta pidvyŝenu zatrymku čakluvannja.
en: Your spells deal more damage and have lower spread and increased cast delay.

ukr: Vaši zaklynannja letjatj švydše ta majutj menšyj rozkyd i u vas je zručnyj cilevkazivnyk dlja pryciljuvannja!
en: Your spells fly faster and have lower spread, and you have a handy sightline for aiming!

ukr: Vaši zaklynannja stajutj menš točnymy, a vy na dejakyj čas stajete biljš leğkozajmystymy.
en: Your spells are less accurate and you're more flammable for a time.

ukr: Na dejakyj čas vy ruxajetesja poviljniše.
en: You move slower for a time.

ukr: Na dejakyj čas vy ruxajetesja nevpevneno.
en: Your movement is unsure for a time.
Your projectiles home back to you!

ukr: Myttjevo zasmoktuje snarjady ta istot, ŝo znaxodjatjsja poblyzu, v seredynu polja
en: Sucks nearby projectiles and creatures into the middle of the field instantaneously

ukr: Koly cej macak potrapljaje u voroğa, voroğ takož vypuskaje macak
en: When this tentacle hits an enemy, said enemy will also launch a tentacle
Limits the radius of a projectile's explosion heavily

ukr: Peretvorjuje dovkolyšni ne mağični ridyny na vybuxovyj porox
en: Converts nearby nonmagical liquids into explosive gunpowder

ukr: Čotyry smertonosnyx plazmovyx promeni u formi xresta.\nOberežno, vony možutj poranyty vas takož!
en: Four deadly plasma beams in a cross-shape. Look out, they can hurt you as well!

ukr: Snarjad striljaje plazmovymy promenjamy na vsi boky!
en: A projectile fires plasma beams in all directions!

ukr: Snarjad vypuskaje plazmovyj prominj pry vidskoku
en: A projectile launches a plasma beam upon bouncing

ukr: Snarjad povertajetjsja v toj bik, kudy vy cilytesja
en: A projectile rotates towards the direction you're aiming

ukr:
«Sekret ležytj u muzyci!

Ključ do nebesnoğo zamka — u muzyci vsjoğo svitu...

I, v jakomusj sensi, jak vğori, tak i vnyzu...»
en:
”The secret lies in music!

The key to the heavens' lock is borne from music all over the world.

And in a way, as above, so below...”
Entirely safe (for a given value of safe)

ukr: Voroğy poruč z vamy otrymujutj škodu. Čym menše u vas OZ, tym biljše škoda.
en: Enemies near you take damage, the damage is higher the lower your health gets.

ukr: Cej artefakt, podibnyj na oko, vyprominjuje zlisne sjajvo
en: This eye-shaped artefact projects a malevolent glare

ukr: Kopijuje kožne statyčne zaklynannja-snarjad v palyčci pry čakluvanni
en: Copies every static projectile -type spell in the wand when cast

ukr: Kopijuje dva nastupnyx zaklynannja v palyčci pry čakluvanni
en: Copies the two following spells in the wand when cast

NOTES – use \n for newline: This is used for the names of some alchemically created materials, e.g. blood converted into water → “Water (Transformed)”

ukr: Vy čujete, jak slovo «$0» vidlunjuje i perelyvajetjsja koljoramy
en: You hear the word “$0” echoing and shifting in colours

ukr: Plazmovyj prominj, ŝo specializujetjsja na rizanni materialiv! Takož efektyvnyj v vbyvstvi voroğiv... ta vas.
en: A plasma beam specialized in cutting materials!
Makes plasma beam spell's beam wider

ukr: Poblyzu vas vidkryvajetjsja kiljka čornyx dir!!!
en: Multiple black holes open in your vicinity!!

NOTES – use \n for newline: (Doesn't need to be translated) XBox 360 controller buttons
(Doesn't need to be translated) XBox 360 controller buttons
(Doesn't need to be translated) XBox 360 controller buttons
(Doesn't need to be translated) XBox 360 controller buttons

for options menu - rebinding controller actions
label for rebinding keys in options
for options menu - rebinding dragging modifier

ukr: Ŝorazu, koly vy vidvidujete novu oblastj, vy zciljujete 60 zdorov'ja.
en: Every time you visit a new area, you regain 60 health.

ukr: Nova oblastj dosjağnuta! Vy otrymujete 60 zdorov'ja.
en: New area reached! You regain 60 health.

ukr: Jakŝo palyčka maje biljše niž 50 many, vsja mana, ŝo perevyŝuje cju mežu, peretvorjujetjsja na dodatkovu škodu
en: If the wand has more than 50 mana, all mana over that is converted into additional damage

ukr: Jakŝo v bezposerednij blyzjkosti vid snarjada z'javljajetjsja dijsna cilj, snarjad teleportujetjsja prjamo na neï
en: If a valid target appears somewhere in the proximity of a projectile, the projectile will teleport right on top of the target

ukr: Zoloto, ŝo vypadaje z voroğiv, vybuxaje koly znykaje, pidbyrajetjsja abo joğo torkajutjsja inši voroğy!
en: Gold dropped by enemies explodes when it disappears, is picked up or touched by other enemies!

ukr: Vsi vybuxovi zaklynannja, zastosovani vamy poblyzu, myttjevo vybuxajutj
en: All nearby explosive spells cast by you instantly detonate

NOTES – use \n for newline: debugish message, used to tell the player that a screenshot has been taken and saved to a location on the disk

ukr: Zmušuje čotyry dyskovi pyly obertatysja navkolo snarjada
en: Makes four sawblades rotate around a projectile

ukr: Zmušuje čotyry voğnjani kuli obertatysja navkolo snarjada
en: Makes four fireballs rotate around a projectile

ukr: Zmušuje čotyry... jaderni bomby(?!) obertatysja navkolo snarjada
en: Makes four… nukes(?!) rotate around a projectile

ukr: Zmušuje čotyry plazmovi promeni obertatysja navkolo snarjada
en: Makes four plasma beams rotate around a projectile

ukr: Zmušuje čotyry kopiï snarjada obertatysja navkolo njoğo
en: Makes four copies of a projectile rotate around it

ukr: Čakluje kopiju nastupnoğo zaklynannja u vašij palyčci
en: Casts a copy of the next spell in your wand

ukr: Čakluje kopiju ostannjoğo zaklynannja u vašij palyčci
en: Casts a copy of the last spell in your wand

ukr: Prokljattja vidstupylo, ale u vas zalyšylysja skarby, nadani nym.
en: The curse has gone away, but so have the treasures it grants.

ukr: Čas perezarjadžannja palyčky stanovytj rivno 1,5 sekundy
en: The reload time of the wand is set to exactly 1.5 seconds

ukr: Summons a tiny ethereal being to your help. It may cast stronger spells depending on how much damage you have suffered.
en: Summons a tiny ethereal being to your help. It may cast stronger spells depending on how much damage you have suffered.
NOTES – use \n for newline: The first sentence has already been translated previously. Second sentence is new.

ukr: Cej artefakt može vidkryty vam potencial palyčok navitj bez zdibnostej...
en: This artefact can open the potential of wands to you even without perks...

ukr: Nazva može buty biljš vlučnoju, niž vy dumajete.
en: The name may be more apt than one thinks.

ukr: Zručna korobka dlja perenesennja poroškopodibnyx materialiv.
en: A handy box for carrying powdery materials.

ukr: Zručna torbynka dlja perenesennja poroškopodibnyx materialiv.
en: A handy bag for carrying powdery materials.

ukr: Zručnyj mišečok dlja perenesennja poroškopodibnyx materialiv.
en: A handy pouch for carrying powdery materials.

ukr: Zručnyj mišečok dlja perenesennja poroškopodibnyx materialiv.
en: A handy sack for carrying powdery materials.

ukr: Vyklykaje ŝaslyvoğo minjjona, jakyj čas vid času z'ïdatyme voroži snarjady.
en: Summons a happy minion who'll eat enemy projectile every now and then, and grant you temporary extra damage.

ukr: Na dejakyj čas zbiljšuje vašu škodu.
en: Your damage is boosted slightly for a time.

ukr: Voroğy pislja smerti zalyšajutj po sobi duxa, jakyj zavdaje škody na nevelykij diljanci.
en: Dying creatures leave behind a spirit that deals damage in a small area.

ukr: Vy otrymujete dodatkovyj šans zavdavaty krytyčnoğo udaru, poky poruč z vamy je voroğy.
en: You gain additional chance to deal critical hits as long as there are enemies near you.

ukr: Nakladaje na snarjad prokljattja, jake zmušuje cilj, v jaku vlučyv snarjad, znyknuty
en: Imbues a projectile with a curse that makes the target hit by the projectile to waste away
Summons a chaotic flock of spicy ducks

ukr: Vytračaje 5% vašoğo potočnoğo zolota i dodaje snarjadu škody proporcijno vytračenij kiljkosti zolota
en: Spends 5% of your current gold and adds damage to a projectile proportional to the amount spent

ukr: Vyklykaje ŝaslyvoğo minjjona, jakyj čas vid času z'ïdatyme voroži snarjady.
en: Summons a happy minion who'll eat enemy projectile every now and then.

NOTES – use \n for newline: Please confirm, that these are correct. Previous translations lacked the ': $0' -part from the end

ukr: Vy otrymujete na 25% biljše škody vid snarjadiv.
en: You take 25% extra damage from projectiles.

ukr: Vy otrymujete na 25% biljše škody vid vybuxiv.
en: You take 25% extra damage from explosions.

ukr: Vy otrymujete na 25% biljše škody vid atak blyžnjoğo boju.
en: You take 25% extra damage from melee attacks.

ukr: Vy otrymujete na 25% biljše škody vid elektryky.
en: You take 25% extra damage from electricity.

ukr: Cilj, v jaku vlučyv snarjad, pevnyj čas otrymuje na 25% biljše škody vid snarjadiv
en: Target hit by a projectile takes 25% extra projectile damage for a time

ukr: Cilj, v jaku vlučyv snarjad, pevnyj čas otrymuje na 25% biljše škody vid vybuxiv
en: Target hit by a projectile takes 25% extra explosion damage for a time

ukr: Cilj, v jaku potrapljaje snarjad, pevnyj čas otrymuje na 25% biljše škody vid blyžnjoğo boju
en: Target hit by a projectile takes 25% extra melee damage for a time

ukr: Cilj, v jaku potrapljaje snarjad, pevnyj čas otrymuje na 25% biljše škody vid elektryky
en: Target hit by a projectile takes 25% extra electricity damage for a time

ukr: Vyklykaje ğiğantsjkoğo xrobaka, ŝob na mytj spryčynyty xaos!
en: Summons a giant worm to cause havoc for a moment!

ukr: Čorna dira z aktyvatorom zakinčennja diï
Poviljna sfera porožneči, jaka poğlynaje vsi pereškody j čakluje inše zaklynannja, koly zakinčujetjsja
en: A slow orb of void that eats through all obstacles and casts another spell as it expires

NOTES – use \n for newline: Reference to the “hunger clock”/”food clock” game mechanic in roguelike games: https://www.gridsagegames.com/blog/2014/12/importance-roguelike-food-clocks/

ukr: Vy zavdajete biljše škody, čym biljše vy syti, ale vy počynajete vtračaty zdorov'ja, jakŝo vaš šlunok porožnij.
en: You inflict more damage the more satiated you are, but you start losing health if your stomach is empty.

ukr:
Rozpljuŝ svoï oči, ja baču
Tvoï oči rozpljuŝeni
Ne maskujsja peredi mnoju
Vyjdy u vidkrytyj svit
en:
Open your eyes, I see
Your eyes are open
Wear no disguise for me
Come into the open
Gives a projectile a trail of rainbow

ukr: Zleğka dzyžčytj. Cikavo, ŝo bude, jakŝo joğo kopnuty...
en: It hums slightly. What happens if you kick it, you wonder...

ukr: Vyğljadaje tak, niby vin može vytrymaty vyprobuvannja eonamy.
en: It looks like it could stand the test of aeons.

ukr: z mojeï krovi... z mojeï krovi... z mojeï krovi... z mojeï krovi... z mojeï krovi...
en: from my blood... from my blood... from my blood... from my blood...

NOTES – use \n for newline: see e.g. stat_depth. This is stat that keeps track of how many times in a row player has beaten the game. Streaks is the common english gaming lingo phrase

ukr: Na dejakyj čas vy otrymujete pole, ŝo zavdaje škody voroğam poblyzu.
en: You gain a field that deals damage to nearby enemies for a time.

ukr: Voroğy poblyzu vas otrymujutj pole, ŝo zavdaje vam škody, jakŝo vy nadto blyzjko.
en: Enemies near you gain fields that deal damage to you if you get close.

ukr: Xrobaky vtikajutj vid vas. Xrobaky ta lukki biljše ne rujnujutj miscevistj pid čas ryttja.
en: Worms run away from you, and worm and lukki enemies no longer destroy terrain while burrowing.
A magical bolt with rejuvenative powers

ukr: Biljšistj palyčok budutj bez tasuvannja. Palyčkam u vašomu inventari takož bude prybrano tasuvannja.
en: Most of the wands will be non shuffling. The wands you carry with you turn into non-shufflers too.

NOTES – use \n for newline: for progress menu - shows how many times player has been killed by the enemy

ukr: Snarjad, ŝo zazvyčaj maje vidskok, vtračaje joğo
en: A normally bouncy projectile stops doing so

NOTES – use \n for newline: New Game$1 -> New Game+ or ++ or +++...

ukr: Kažutj, ŝo vin volodije syloju, jaku prosti smertni navrjad čy možutj osjağnuty, ne kažučy vže pro te, ŝob vykorystaty
en: It is said to possess powers which mere mortals can scarcely comprehend, let alone utilize

ukr: Snarjad, jakyj vybuxaje, peretvorjuučysj na lypke misyvo
en: A projectile that explodes into a sticky mess
Turns a wounded enemy into stone

ukr: Krytyčne popadannja peretvorjuje voroğa na kaminj
en: A critical hit turns an enemy into stone

ukr: Krytyčne popadannja peretvorjuje poranenoğo voroğa na kaminj
en: A critical hit turns a wounded enemy into stone

ukr: Vyklykaje masyvnoğo xrobaka, ŝob na mytj spryčynyty xaos!
en: Summons a massive worm to cause havoc for a moment!

ukr: Vidštovxuje snarjady, ŝo letjatj, u vyğljadi vuzjkoğo konusa
en: Pushes incoming projectiles away in a narrow cone formation

ukr: Koly vy nablyžajetesja do nebezpeky, u vas z'javljajutjsja ğrybkovi narosty.
en: When near danger, you sprout fungal growths.
Summons a lukki minion to your help.

ukr: Vbyvajučy voroğa, vy popovnjujete častynu svojeï syly levitaciï.
en: Killing an enemy makes you replenish some of your levitation power.
Your spells destroy ground more efficiently.

ukr: Slyz poblyzu vas spontanno peretvorjujetjsja na ğrybkovyx istot.
en: Slime near you spontaneously turns into fungal creatures.

ukr: Ğrybkovi istoty vidrodžujutjsja z trupiv ubytyx vamy voroğiv.
en: Fungal creatures spawn from the corpses of enemies killed by you.

ukr: Nevelykyj plavajučyj snarjad, jakyj letytj u bik najblyžčyx istot.
en: A small, floating projectile that homes towards nearby creatures

ukr: Snarjad letytj do cili, perebuvajučy poruč z neju
en: A projectile flies towards targets when near them

ukr: Teper vono svitytjsja z vysokoju intensyvnistju...
en: It glows with high intensity now...
The essence of the Sun, crystallized.

ukr: Vono ŝe ne povnistju vyroslo, ale vže vyprominjuje teplo.
en: It's still not fully grown but radiates heat.

ukr:
«Odyn v stavku
Odyn na derevi
Odyn na vidstupi
Odyn pid soncem»
en:
”One in the lake
One in the tree
One on the island
One under the sun”

ukr:
«Toj, ŝo nyžče, sluxaje moï pisni...
 
G D# G E A
 
E C B G# F»
en:
”The one below listens to my songs...
 
G D# G E A
 
E C B G# F”

ukr:
«Sered velykyx Alximičnyx zveršenj je taki, jaki,
xoč i ne rivni Velykomu Tvoru, vse ž duže šanujutjsja
za božestvennu sylu, jaku vony darujutj tomu, xto dosjağne uspixu
v osvojenni ïxnjoï Syly.

Toj, pro koğo ja budu ğovoryty, zaklykaje do Zerna velykoï nadiï, zaxovanoğo ğlyboko v grunti cijeï Zemli...»
en:
”Among the great Alchemical endeavours there are some that,
while not equal to the Great Work, nonetheless are revered greatly
for the deific potence they instill to whomsoever succeeds
in harnessing their Power.

The One I am to discuss calls for a Seed of great promise, hidden deep within the Soil of this Earth...”

ukr: «...Probuditj Nasinnja zi snu, dozvolyvšy jomu vvibraty v sebe promeni Soncja, na veršyni mynulyx cyvilizacij...»
en: ”...Bring the slumbering Seed to life by letting it soak in the rays of the Sun, on the pinnacle of past civilizations...”

ukr: «...Alximičnyj proces vymağaje velykoğo Voğnju i Tepla, dlja cjoğo\npokladitj Kaminj u Voğnennu Zemlju i proveditj joğo peretvorennja za dopomoğoju velykoğo mağičnoğo Tepla Rujnuvannja...»
en: ”...The Alchemical process requires great Fire and Heat; for this purpose,\nlay the Stone in Fiery Earth and bring forth its transformation with great magical Heat of Destruction...”

ukr: «...Po zaveršennju, vono bude pidtrymuvaty žyttja; dlja cjoğo joğo Tvorinnja potrebuje značnoï kiljkosti\nŽyttjevoï Syly. Nexaj Jajce poğlyne SOTNJU tvoïx VOROĞIV i vyp'je ïxnju KROV...»
en: ”...Once finished, It will sustain life; to this end, its Creation asks for a substantial amount\nof Life Force. Let the Egg engulf One Hundred of your Foes and drink their Blood...”

ukr: «...Jak ostannij krok, viddajte zarodku krystalizovani Sutnosti Čotyrjox Styxij.\nAle budjte oberežnymy, bo zarodok sxyljnyj do zğubnoğo vplyvu...»
en: ”...As a final step, imbue the Youngling with the crystallized Essences of\nthe Four Elements. But beware, for the Youngling is susceptible to corruptive influence...”

ukr: «Koly Ključ vysluxaje tebe, prynesy joğo dodomu...\nOdyn dim u nebi, za nevydymymy prostomu oku sxodamy...\nOdyn dim u pidzemnomu sviti, pid morjamy mağmy...»
en: ”Once the Key has listened to you, bring it home...\nOne home in the sky, beyond the invisible steps...\nOne home in the underworld, below seas of magma...”

ukr: «Cja mašyna ne sxoža na žodnu z tyx, ŝo ja bačyv raniše. Hiisi stvoryly ïï? Čy vona zavždy bula tut?»
en: ”This machinery is unlike any I've seen before. Did the Hiisi create it? Or was it always here?”

ukr: Vyklykaje kiljce z 8 noživ, ŝo zvužujetjsja
en: A shrinking ring of 8 knives is summoned
A magical ball of frozen fire

ukr: «Jak i vse inše, kožne nebesne tilo takož maje svoğo dvijnyka.\nZa kožnoju zolotoju zirkoju stoïtj temna zağadka, a za kožnym sribljastym misjacem — porožnja tinj.»
en: ”As with everything else, every celestial body also has its counterpart.\nFor every golden star is a dark enigma, and for every silvery moon there is a hollow shadow.”

ukr: Budj-jaki minjjony, ŝo z'javljajutjsja vam na dopomoğu, majutj biljše zdorov'ja ta zavdajutj biljše škody.
en: Any minions spawned to your aid have increased damage output and health.

ukr: Jakŝo zupynytysja na mytj, to možna vidčuty svoje misceznaxodžennja vidnosno Ğory.
en: If you stop for a moment, you can sense your location relative to the Mountain.

ukr: Stare poğlynajetjsja, ŝob na joğo misce pryjšlo nove
en: The old are devoured for the new to take their place

ukr: Nove serce svitu perebuvaje v rivnovazi
en: The new heart of the world is at balance

ukr: Jak vğori, tak i vnyzu, ale...
Nove serce svitu roste z porokom u joğo centri
en: The new heart of the world grows with corruption at its center
Summons a box of explosive matter
Summons a large box of explosive matter

ukr: Istoty, ŝo znaxodjatjsja poruč z vamy, otrymujutj možlyvistj vxodyty v portaly Svjatoï Ğory.
en: Creatures near you gain the ability to enter the Holy Mountain portals.
It seems to trickle with blood...

ukr: Vaši opory j zaxysni zdibnosti tymčasovo vymkneni.
en: Your resistances and protective perks are disabled temporarily.

ukr: Cej artefakt vkrytyj ğravijuvannjam u formi not i puljsuje v postijnomu tempi.\nCe zvuky viddalenoï muzyky?
en: This artefact is covered in note-shaped engravings and is pulsing at a steady pace.\nIs that the sound of distant music?

ukr: Vy otrymujete artefakt, jakyj dozvoljaje vyklykaty nebesnu ljutj.
en: You gain an artefact that allows you to call the celestial rage.
Creates an immensely powerful entity. Can be cast only once
Creates an immensely powerful entity. Can be cast only once

ukr: Voroğy vybuxajutj pislja smerti, ale vy nevrazlyvi do vybuxiv.
en: Enemies explode upon death, but you gain immunity to explosive damage.
The world is at a balance
The world is overburdened by light
You bleed flammable gas instead of blood.
Everything is glowing in a mysterious light...!

ukr:
This mod has been built with a newer version of the modding interface.
A newer version of the game might be required.
Or maybe the mod developer is just using a new version of the game,
and everything is compatible.
en:
This mod has been built with a newer version of the modding interface.
A newer version of the game might be required.
Or maybe the mod developer is just using a new version of the game,
and everything is compatible.

ukr: Plazmovi promeni vylitajutj u X-podibnij formi
en: Plasma beams fly in an X-shaped pattern

ukr: U vas je postijnyj plazmovyj prominj, ale vy poviljniše čaklujete zaklynannja
en: You constantly fire a devastating plasma beam, but you fire spells much slower

ukr:
“One in the pond
One in the tree
One on the ledge
One under the sun”
en:
“One in the pond
One in the tree
One on the ledge
One under the sun”

ukr:
Vitajemo v onovlenni «Epiloğ» dlja Noita!
Noita kolysj bula u dočasnomu dostupi ta my xočemo peredaty vam vdjačnistj,
vdjačnistj vsim tym, xto ğrav u Noita u perši ïï roky. Vaši vidğuky duže cinni dlja nas!
A dlja vsix novyx ğravciv... Vitajemo ta bažajemo udači!
- Rozrobnyky

A perekladač djakuje vam za vykorystannja perekladu!
en:
Welcome to Noita Epilogue Update!
Noita used be an Early Access game, so we want to send a huge thank you to all of you
who played Noita during its first year. Your feedback has been invaluable!
And to all the new Noita players... Welcome and best of luck!
- Devs

ukr:
Vitajemo v onovlenni «Epiloğ 2» dlja Noita!
Noita kolysj bula u dočasnomu dostupi ta my xočemo peredaty vam vdjačnistj,
vdjačnistj vsim tym, xto ğrav u Noita u perši ïï roky. Vaši vidğuky duže cinni dlja nas!
A dlja vsix novyx ğravciv... Vitajemo ta bažajemo udači!
- Rozrobnyky

A perekladač djakuje vam za vykorystannja perekladu!
en:
Welcome to Noita Epilogue 2 Update!
Noita used be an Early Access game, so we want to send a huge thank you to all of you
who played Noita during its first year. Your feedback has been invaluable!
And to all the new Noita players... Welcome and best of luck!
- Devs

ukr:
”The four Essences represent the four Elements that form this visible World...
Imbued with their Terrible Power, one may do great deeds,
but one should be Afraid of their destructive Might. To this end,
we have Devised a way to remove these Dangerous Forces; seek it in the West and East.

A Legend also tells that all the Elements originated from the Egg of Sky and return to It one day...”
en:
”The four Essences represent the four Elements that form this visible World...
Imbued with their Terrible Power, one may do great deeds,
but one should be Afraid of their destructive Might. To this end,
we have Devised a way to remove these Dangerous Forces; seek it in the West and East.

A Legend also tells that all the Elements originated from the Egg of Sky and return to It one day...”

ukr:
”One of my brethren ran away in order to escape our predicament ...
They felt our understanding of this world was to be forbidden.
They hid something here, in this room, but...
...I lack the ability to truly see what is here!”
en:
”One of my brethren ran away in order to escape our predicament ...
They felt our understanding of this world was to be forbidden.
They hid something here, in this room, but...
...I lack the ability to truly see what is here!”

ukr:
”In my dream I saw a great Diamond...
It invited me within, offering me Grand Treasures.
This it said to me:
'If you wish to follow the Path I show you here, you must bring me one of these Two:
a terrible Curse of Avarice, or the most Singular being in this realm.'
I do not fully understand these words, but I still see the Diamond in my mind's eye...”
en:
”In my dream I saw a great Diamond...
It invited me within, offering me Grand Treasures.
This it said to me:
'If you wish to follow the Path I show you here, you must bring me one of these Two:
a terrible Curse of Avarice, or the most Singular being in this realm.'
I do not fully understand these words, but I still see the Diamond in my mind's eye...”
